The results are trickling in, going by uploads by INEC.
In Abaji chairmanship election, out of 485 results being expected, 410 have been submitted as at 7am on Sunday.
In Abaji, results have been submitted in 109 out of 135 polling units.
Gwagwalada had 268 of 338 results in.
Kuje had 204 of 262. In Kwali, only 45 out of 201 have been uploaded.
In Abuja municipal, 768 of 1401 results had been submitted to the INEC portal.



